    h3 Getting Started:

    h4 Step 1 &mdash; Download:

    p There are multiple ways to get Caramel, choose from the following for what seems the best option for you.

    hr

    div(class='row')
        div(class='box col-6')
            h3 Download
            p Pre-Compiled Latest Version of Caramel, includes all the bells and whistles, with some documentation thrown in for good measure.
            br
