    hr

    h4 Step 2 &mdash; Play

    p. 
        Now that you have Caramel at your finger tips, you should probably see what we have to offer! Available 
        a(href='showcase.html') here
        , is a list of all of our features. To see the code of a specific element, right click the element and click 'Inspect Element'. If your browser doesn't support this feature, you can right click the page and click 'View Source' instead.
        br

    p.
        Ready to get started? We've included a template that already has Caramel built-in. To access the template, locate 
        code template.html
        , open it in your editor of choice, and code away!

    p. 
        If you wish to encorporate Caramel into your existing documents, paste the following lines into your document's 
        code &lt;head&gt;
        section.

